S.FORM: Togo hya' ga cyux maki' tay 8 00 N, 1 10 E na Xweco syuw. kwara' kinghciyan niya' 56,785 sq km (maki' tay 126ginkgan kin wahci') (kinwhci' niya' ga 54,385 sq km, kinwhci' na lawsayan wsilung hya' ga 2,400 sq km) Kinkhmayan kwara' squliq hya' ga 7,756,937. Pinbcyan naha' sni' naha' rhzyal hya' iy pqmahun hya' ga 67.40%, lhlahuy hya' ga 4.90%, sni' naha' sa pptzyuwaw sa bzinah hya' ga 27.70%. spzyang qalang na Kokka' spzyang naha' krahu' qalang hya' ga Lome. snyan kinramat inlungan na Kokka' snyan kinramat inlungan na Kokka' hya' ga 27 na tay spayat byacing na qutux kawas. mrhuw Kokka' mrhuw Kokka' ta' misuw hya' ga Faure Gnassingbé, aring ryax 4 squ byacing tay 5 sa kawas 2005 lga, musa' spazyang balay ms'rux kya la. cinkhulan sa knita' sa brbiru' CIA 外交部
